### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:5550/api/v1
@churchId = church-uuid-here
@branchId = branch-uuid-here
@memberId = member-uuid-here
@userId = user-uuid-here

### List members of a church
GET {{baseUrl}}/churches/{{churchId}}/members

### List members of a branch
GET {{baseUrl}}/churches/{{churchId}}/branches/{{branchId}}/members

### Search members
GET {{baseUrl}}/churches/{{churchId}}/members/search?query=christian

### Create member (Assign user to church)
POST {{baseUrl}}/churches/{{churchId}}/members
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "{{userId}}",
  "branchId": "{{branchId}}",
  "role": "member"
}

### Get member details
GET {{baseUrl}}/churches/{{churchId}}/members/{{memberId}}

### Update member
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/churches/{{churchId}}/members/{{memberId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "role": "pastor",
  "status": "active"
}

### Delete member
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/churches/{{churchId}}/members/{{memberId}}
